title: Protect
content:
Protect may refer to:

  • Dragonfire protection, protection against dragonfire
  • Equipment
    • God protection, equipment that makes monsters following a respective god unaggressive towards you in the God Wars Dungeon and Wilderness God Wars Dungeon
    • Slayer equipment, specific equipment that protects you from negative effects or to finish off a monster at low health
    • Tier-5 Shayzien armour, the full set that protects you from the poison attacks of lizardman shamans
    • Warm clothes, warm or winter-themed equipment that reduces damage taken from the Wintertodt
    • Yak-hide armour, mainly used in the Fremennik Isles quest to mitigate the attacks of Ice Trolls
  • Heat protection, protection against desert heat
  • Orbs of protection, a quest item used during Tree Gnome Village
  • Protection prayers, prayers that grant immunity from Magic, Ranged or Melee attacks dependent on the respective prayer
    • Protect Item, a prayer that lets you keep one extra item upon dying
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
